casebody.data:
Francienna GRANT, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
DAN'S AUTO BODY, LLC and Dan Rusco, Defendants. M-16/17 September Term 2018
080491 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-16) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-17) is denied.
